What a great experience! Astoria Seafood and Grill seemed underwhelming from the outside, but it is anything but underwhelming once you enter! The food was great, the service was fantastic! Our waiter, Javier, was attentive, warm and genuine. The seafood was fresh and perfectly prepared. The prices were extremely reasonable and the portions were generous. If you happen to find this hidden gem while in Astoria, do yourself a favor and stop in. You won’t regret it. Absolutely delightful experience with great atmosphere, food, and service. I will definitely return!

A great find!
